headline: Fair Isaac (FICO) Valuation Check After Recent Share Price Pullback
summary: Fair Isaac (FICO) is back in focus after recent trading left the shares about 12% lower over the past month and roughly 17% lower over the past year. This has prompted fresh interest from valuation minded investors. See our latest analysis for Fair Isaac.
